headline: Home Builder Stocks Start 2026 With a Bang. Why They Could Have Room to Run.
summary: Home builder stocks are having a hopeful start to the year.  There are plenty of reasons to expect that 2026 will be better for the housing market.  The  exchange-traded fund, which includes home builders and related companies, is up 2.8% so far this year.
